node.text:
Parents everywhere are wondering why it’s more fun to make the bed and feed the dog in the @fisherprice Little People Big Helpers Home than in real life! 

Swipe through for your kids to see Kabil’s imagination at work as his group of little friends eat lunch, play hide and seek, and enjoy a picnic in the yard! 

What chores do you wish were only make-believe?

node.text:
Ready, set, RACE! @xicana_mama helps Lali and Soona launch cars off the @FisherPrice Little People Launch & Loop Raceway. 

Parents, swipe to see the twins take on the racetrack’s steep drop and winding curves. Then tell us your favorite part below! (Spoiler: We loved every moment.)
